profile:
Ashley Gold is a certified and accredited home staging designer providing professional services to both realtors and homeowners alike. Having established staging opportunities with various real estate developers, project management companies as well as with realtors. 

She has personally applied her talents and design skills all across North America and has planned and designed diverse sets of living spaces ranging from condo size dwellings to 10,000sq ft homes each having their own set of challenges.
